<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><strong>山药小米粥</strong></p>
<p><strong>材料：</strong>小米50克、粥米80克、山药150克。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180930/2e8e610a1b614df58e3c01ece726ef18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>制作：</strong></p>
<p>1.将小米和粥米清洗干净;山药去皮,切成滚刀;放入压力锅中，加入清水约1300克。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180930/ea2a297c52b44cd18f6f815958176f3d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>2.盖好锅盖，设置加压12分钟。解压后放几粒枸杞，搅拌煮开即可。</p>
<p><strong>注：</strong>枸杞最后放，因煮久就无味了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180930/011a1b288b6040f8b3e7c187caa018f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180930/a035e1da4e7e422890430a5a20d71851.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜小鸡炖三鲜，咱不用一滴油！太鲜了，上桌就扫空！
http://www.sohu.com/a/274671020_257484	83163
<p>小鸡炖三鲜，类似东北的小鸡炖蘑菇，或者是黄焖鸡腿饭，烧法都大致相同，但就那一点细微的区别就有着不同的口味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/ffa2661cb9b34858a3fa469e34e9ea27.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>这会做的这道菜，我没有用一滴油，就是将鸡皮上的油脂慢慢地煎出来，这样处理特别的干香有滋味，再加上蘑菇木耳黄花菜的鲜，真是太美味了，写菜谱这会想想口生津，明天还要整一锅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/c2049ef3138045e6b782c7110b1c16d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>材料：鸡腿3只、香菇15朵、木耳一把、黄花菜一把、大葱一节，蒜头1个、生姜一块、花椒一撮</strong></p>
<p><strong>制作：</strong></p>
<p>1.香菇、木耳和黄花菜提前泡好，摘洗干净。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/833e0fd48d8f4418b80b10d8a2e9d1f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>2.鸡腿处理干净，剁成大块。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/be0672616c424867b96989952d2899c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3.锅里不放油，用中小火慢慢的煎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/d56f2c1f7c854c06879fd061a6140d9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4.煎到鸡肉微变黄，没有水分的时候下花椒、大葱和生姜。</p>
<p>5.当香料出香味时，倒入酱油。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/7d19fa2bfb79476192c9f14901eba683.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>6.这时锅可能会有点干，点少量的泡香菇的水湿润一下。</p>
<p>7.翻炒均匀上色，加入三鲜：蘑菇、木耳和黄花菜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/a58cfdce89b14f3192593d7cfc86e50c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>8.翻炒出香味，倒入泡香菇的水漫过食材。</p>
<p>9.盖上锅盖大火煮开，转中火炖。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/8fefaea6066447848fc98613477d7645.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>10.炖到鸡肉变软时，放大蒜瓣，并加盐调味。继续再炖上几分钟到蒜瓣变软就可享用了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/f0093ddbc2df43fd800525cf42f15867.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>细微小语：</strong></p>
<p>1.喜欢用汤泡饭，不要收汁过干。</p>
<p>2.最后也可再加些土豆和胡萝卜炖上一大锅， 有点类似黄焖鸡腿饭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181112/5d6d81a6affa414a84b25ebede2f66ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>